      "rationale": "Code verification performed via manufactured-solution patch tests for linear elastic beam bending and contact mechanics. Results match analytical solutions within 0.1% for all three solver instances. Ansys solver verification suite results (ANSYS Mechanical Verification Manual, Release 2022 R2) document convergence for analogous structural contact problems. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
