      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/criteria/validation-relevance-level2",
      "rationale": "Validation activity is a direct comparison of FEA predictions to ASTM F1717 bench testing of the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw design under the identical loading protocol. The COU is prediction of F1717 compression-bending performance; the validation activity IS the F1717 test. Validation domain (bench test) matches COU domain (regulatory submission supporting F1717 performance claims). No extrapolation beyond validation envelope is required. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    }
